- if (can? :edit, @dataset)
  .idb-dashboard.panel.panel-warning
    -#.panel-heading
    -#  %span(class="metadata-label" )Dataset Dashboard
    .panel-body
      %span(class="glyphicon glyphicon-eye-open" )
      %span(class="metadata-label" ) Visibility:
      = @dataset.visibility
      %br
      %span(class="glyphicon glyphicon-triangle-right" )
      %span(class="metadata-label" ) Progress:
      - if @dataset.publication_state == Databank::PublicationState::DRAFT || (can? :manage, @dataset)
        Edit the dataset description and file set as needed, then save to review before publishing.  You will be able to come back here to edit.
      - else
        You can edit the description for the dataset, but you would need to contact the
        %a(href="/help#contact" )Research Data Service
        if you need to change, update, or add files for any reason.
